    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Looks like nomachine uses port 4000, which is the same port that Prysm's beacon chain serves.\r\n\r\nSuggestion:\r\n- Set beacon chain to use a non default port grpc. `--rpc-port=4001`\r\n- Set validator to use this new address. `--beacon-rpc-provider=127.0.0.1:4001`\r\n\r\nAlternatively, set nomachine to not use port 4000. I don't know how to do this so I'm not suggesting it. ",
